93411238088744/IMG_5654.png?ex=6a37b0eb&is=6a365f6b&hm=adb4ba9b56e7d0b1e098a2a2913b8ae3da0d3c60c78eb633c3670baaa2f4a517&"}, {"id": "1218493411716366386", "filename": "IMG_5655.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1197481, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1173463482503536711/1218493411716366386/IMG_5655.png?ex=6a37b0eb&is=6a365f6b&hm=aec9cb6ea565ee16dcd270b355283c7d8c7004de02ea3f805d663fcd58778139&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218493826394751047", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "這段基本可以確定入夢改變的那些場景都是僅限於喚醒體的意識中，守密人進入的是喚醒體的意識構築的過去的場景（夢），並不是真正跨越了時間線", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:39:26.733000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218494384060760075", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "author_bot": false, "content": "好耶", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:41:39.691000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218494435520942161", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "感覺確實很像這樣，因為守密人確實解開了阿格里帕的心結，讓他們走出了迷宮。\n但從歷史上看的話阿格里帕還是死在了那場奴隸暴亂裡，並沒有逃走。", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:41:51.960000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:42:09.896000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["546511962977337344"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1218208835123151009", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218495120895246389", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "阿格的劇情我是覺得有點奇怪，因為在我看來有點是入夢到彌薩格的(女?)學生中，去解了阿格建造的心的迷宮，所以更沒有改變歷史的問題", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:44:35.366000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:47:45.291000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["777861907973406731"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1218494435520942161", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218497102905081876", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "我比較在意的是阿格她離開迷宮的時間點到底是\n1. 之前就從迷宮裡出來了然後才加入彌撒格大學\n2. 直到守密人入夢之後她才從迷宮裡離開，然後成為大學的喚醒體", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:52:27.914000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:56:09.855000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218497897906176010", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "2的話就會很有矛盾點，因為這樣的話守密人儘管入的是女學生的夢那他也不應該認識阿格，可是守密人在夢裡看到阿格的時候有認出她也就是說他是認識阿格的\n那這樣的話情況應該是1（", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:55:37.457000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218498123626844180", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "沒離開吧，大約就是死在裡面，然後被融蝕，後來被挖出之類的?", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:56:31.273000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["777861907973406731"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1218497102905081876", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218498248738738246", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且迷宮不是阿格建的，她是迷宮之主但也是被人丟進來的", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:57:01.102000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218498419086069790", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "我是認為之前應該就有那位女學生，但這樣的話守密人又好像沒改變到什麼，所以我才覺得有改變歷史\n當然既然是夢也可能是阿格幻想著有人能救她出來(心靈方面", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:57:41.716000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:58:29.942000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218498653417898054", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "她是被尤烏哈希殺掉的，所以被丟進迷宮應該是變成喚醒體之後（？", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:58:37.585000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1218498123626844180", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218498919529451630", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "或者是因為迷宮他才變成了喚醒體（說不定也有這可能", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T09:59:41.031000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218499048193921044", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "我是覺得迷宮更像是她作為喚醒體的特質之一，剛好符合當下的心境?", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T10:00:11.707000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218500854588641311", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "嗯⋯⋯如果整個有關迷宮的設定其實都是阿格的夢的話那感覺也說得通⋯？", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T10:07:22.385000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1218501157606002778", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且這樣的話也能解釋時間線矛盾的問題", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T10:08:34.630000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
